texts: Please note that taxi ranks have recently been appointed at the following locations
Royal Albert Hall, SW7 for 5 cabs. This rank is available between mid-day and 3am.
Wells Terrace, Finsbury Park (north side of station) for 3 cabs. This is an 'island' rank and may be worked by Haringey sector drivers and All-London drivers.
Creek Road, Deptford for 2 cabs. This rank is available between 8pm and 5am.
Station Square, Petts Wood for 2 cabs. This rank is available between 4pm and 2am.
Centre Court, The Broadway, Wimbledon for 2 cabs. This rank has been relocated to the south of the bus stop area. It is not available Monday to Friday 7am to 10am or from 4pm to 7pm.
Drivers are invited to make every effort to work these ranks during the hours of operation.
